'Set goals to track your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.':{es:'Establece metas para seguir tu progreso. Ej: diario 5x/semana, meditar diario, asistir a una reuni\u00f3n.',fr:'Fixez des objectifs pour suivre votre progression. Ex: journal 5x/semaine, m\u00e9ditation quotidienne, assister \u00e0 une r\u00e9union.',de:'Setze Ziele, um deinen Fortschritt zu verfolgen. Z.B. Tagebuch 5x/Woche, t\u00e4glich meditieren, an einem Treffen teilnehmen.',it:'Stabilisci obiettivi per tracciare i tuoi progressi. Es: diario 5x/settimana, meditare ogni giorno, partecipare a un incontro.',pt:'Defina metas para acompanhar seu progresso. Ex: di\u00e1rio 5x/semana, meditar diariamente, participar de uma reuni\u00e3o.','tr':'Set goals to track your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.','nl':'Stel doelen om uw herstelvoortgang bij te houden. Voorbeelden: 5x per week een dagboek bijhouden, dagelijks mediteren, een vergadering bijwonen.','pl':'Set goals to track your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.','ja':'Set goals to track your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.','ru':'Set goals to track your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.','zh-cn':'设定目标以跟踪 your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.',ko:'Set goals to track your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.',ar:'Set goals to track your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.',hi:'Set goals to track your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.',bn:'Set goals to track your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.',sv:'Stt ml fr att flja din terhmtningsframsteg. Exempel: dagbok 5 ggr/vecka, meditera dagligen, delta i mte.',no:'Sett ml for  spore bedringsprogresjonen din. Eksempler: dagbok 5x/uke, mediter daglig, delta p mte.',da:'St ml for at spore din bedringsfremgang. Eksempler: dagbog 5x/uge, mediter dagligt, deltag i mde.',fi:'Aseta tavoitteita seurataksesi toipumisen edistymist. Esim: pivkirja 5x/vko, meditoi pivittin, osallistu kokoukseen.',el:'Set goals to track your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.',he:'Set goals to track your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.',th:'Set goals to track your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.',vi:'Set goals to track your recovery progress. Examples: journal 5x/week, meditate daily, attend a meeting.',id:'Tetapkan tujuan untuk melacak kemajuan pemulihan Anda. Contoh: jurnal 5x/minggu, meditasi harian, hadiri pertemuan.',ms:'Tetapkan matlamat untuk menjejak kemajuan pemulihan anda. Contoh: jurnal 5x/minggu, meditasi harian, hadiri mesyuarat.',sw:'Weka malengo kufuatilia maendeleo yako ya nafuu. Mifano: andika jarida mara 5 kwa wiki, tafakari kila siku, hudhuria mkutano.',tl:'Magtakda ng mga layunin upang subaybayan ang iyong pag-unlad sa pagbangon. Halimbawa: mag-journal 5x/linggo, magnilay araw-araw, dumalo sa pulong.',ro:'Stabili\u021bi obiective pentru a v\u0103 urm\u0103ri progresul recuper\u0103rii. Exemple: jurnal de 5 ori/s\u0103pt\u0103m\u00e2n\u0103, medita\u021bie zilnic\u0103, participa\u021bi la o \u0219edin\u021b\u0103.',cs:'Stanovte si c\u00edle pro sledov\u00e1n\u00ed sv\u00e9ho pokroku p\u0159i uzdraven\u00ed. P\u0159\u00edklady: den\u00edk 5x/t\u00fddn\u011b, denn\u00ed meditace, \u00fa\u010dast na setk\u00e1n\u00ed.',hu:'T\u0171z\u00f6n ki c\u00e9lokat a gy\u00f3gyul\u00e1si folyamat nyomon k\u00f6vet\u00e9s\u00e9hez. P\u00e9ld\u00e1k: napl\u00f3z\u00e1s heti 5x, napi medit\u00e1ci\u00f3, r\u00e9sv\u00e9tel egy tal\u00e1lkoz\u00f3n.',uk:'\u041f\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0432\u0442\u0435 \u0446\u0456\u043b\u0456 \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0432\u0456\u0434\u0441\u0442\u0435\u0436\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044f \u043f\u0440\u043e\u0433\u0440\u0435\u0441\u0443 \u043e\u0434\u043e\u043b\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044f. \u041f\u0440\u0438\u043a\u043b\u0430\u0434\u0438: \u0436\u0443\u0440\u043d\u0430\u043b 5\u0440/\u0442\u0438\u0436\u0434\u0435\u043d\u044c, \u0449\u043e\u0434\u0435\u043d\u043d\u0430 \u043c\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u0430\u0446\u0456\u044f, \u0432\u0456\u0434\u0432\u0456\u0434\u0443\u0432\u0430\u0442\u0438 \u0437\u0443\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0456\u0447\u0456.'},
